{"tid":1321371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來黑警做嘢真係唔使你教，入商場拉人可以攞正牌！","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:46:56.000Z","uid":149806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ecfcc7284ef1dd54ea69fe5012854d331f99373","tid":1321371,"uid":149806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"//15.7.2019 新城市廣場地契確有警察通行條款<br />\n<br />\n尋晚有警察進入新城市廣場執行職務, 令管理公司引來批評, 另有一番爭議. 翻查新城市廣場於1981年嘅地契 (STTL 143), 入面的確寫有較少見嘅地契條款, 就係&quot;Police Access&quot; 同埋&quot;Police Reporting Centre&quot; 條款 (圖1). &quot;Police Reporting Centre&quot; 條款之後於1984年取消, 但&quot;Police Access&quot; 則保留. 如根據地契, 管理公司的確不能阻止警察進入.<br />\n<br />\n另外要留意返, 小編亦想補充返今朝關於警察進入私有產權地方嘅post, 部份屋苑地契亦會因應&quot;公眾空間&quot;而包含 &quot;警察通行條款&quot; (如圖2) 容許警察進入&quot;公眾空間&quot;執行職務... 如想知道自己屋苑地契有無類似條款, 則可到&quot;田土廳&quot;查冊及搵專業人士提供意見.<br />\n<br />\n當然, 地契條款並唔係法例, 而係契約. 除地契外, 一切亦要跟隨法例處理.//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2418829341710714/posts/2503125239947790?s=576852137&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2418829341710714%2Fposts%2F2503125239947790%3Fs%3D576852137%26sfns%3Dmo&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=58f56043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2418829341710714/posts/2503125239947790?s=576852137&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5f84b33f979ecc68e63b870adc409f644c74ea10","tid":1321371,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"有無法律高人分析下，有呢類地契黑警係未真係可以屈機？要硬入真係無計？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/352235/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%86%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%84%A1%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%